summary: Whiterun in the aftermath of a devastating tornado
descriptionHtml:
EMERGENCY BULLETIN: A catastrophic EF-5 tornado has obliterated Whiterun! The marketplace, all houses, and Dragonsreach...all destroyed! The people of Skyrim are requesting assistance for all those affected by the disaster. Donations accepted by FEMA of Tamriel.

This is a fun mod intended for laughs. ADVISORY: This mod will conflict with quests within Whiterun. Disable mod if you need to complete quests.
author: banzaigtv
